---
// Sección de Valores Corporativos
---

<section id="valores" class="values-section reveal">
  <div class="values-container">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="values-header">
      <span class="values-badge">Nuestros Valores</span>
      <h2 class="values-title">
        Los principios que guían<br/>
        <span class="text-accent">cada acción</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de valores -->
    <div class="values-grid">
      
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--blue">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Integridad</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Actuamos con honestidad y transparencia en cada proceso. 
          Tu confianza es nuestro mayor activo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--green">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Empatía</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Entendemos lo que significa ser migrante. Tratamos cada caso 
          con la sensibilidad que merece.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--purple">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Excelencia</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Buscamos la perfección en cada trámite. No descansamos hasta 
          lograr los mejores resultados para ti.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--orange">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 9V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3l-4 9v11h11.28a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.7l1.38-9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2.3zM7 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Compromiso</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Tu éxito es nuestro éxito. Nos comprometemos al 100% con 
          cada cliente hasta lograr sus objetivos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--teal">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <path d="M12 6v6l4 2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Puntualidad</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Respetamos tu tiempo y los plazos legales. Cumplimos lo que 
          prometemos, siempre a tiempo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon value-icon--pink">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z" />
            <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-title">Responsabilidad</h3>
        <p class="value-desc">
          Asumimos la responsabilidad de cada proceso. Tu tranquilidad 
          depende de nuestra seriedad.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .values-section {
    padding: 0.5rem clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 4rem) 1rem;
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
  }

  .values-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .values-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .values-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .values-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    color: var(--color-black);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .text-accent {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform var(--transition-slow) var(--ease-in-out), box-shadow var(--transition-slow) var(--ease-in-out);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-xl);
    border-color: rgba(0, 27, 72, 0.15);
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-5);
  }

  .value-icon svg {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
  }

  .value-icon--blue {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 27, 72, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 27, 72, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--blue svg { color: var(--color-primary); }

  .value-icon--green {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) 0%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--green svg { color: var(--color-success); }

  .value-icon--purple {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--purple svg { color: #8b5cf6; }

  .value-icon--orange {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15) 0%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--orange svg { color: #f97316; }

  .value-icon--teal {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.15) 0%, rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--teal svg { color: #14b8a6; }

  .value-icon--pink {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.15) 0%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.05) 100%);
  }
  .value-icon--pink svg { color: #ec4899; }

  .value-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .value-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .value-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
